# references/ directory (inside the skill)
#
# Put supporting docs the model can read to understand the skill's context: pattern
# guides, external API docs, design decisions. Reference them from SKILL.md with
# relative links so they load on demand.
#
# This folder lives inside skills/<skill-name>/ so those relative links keep working.
#
# Delete this file when you add your first real reference, or remove the folder if
# you need none.
